{
  "stem": "18654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because they did a lot of charity work, but not immediate charity work-- you know, not in-- not visible charity work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their-- their name was Worms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry, I'm speaking German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was also Lowenthal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her maiden name was Lowenthal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think they were distantly related to my mother because, as I mentioned before, her name was Lowenthal as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were-- they're very wealthy people living in London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The old lady is, of course, dead by now but the Lowenthals still exist here in London today.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because nobody-- there was nobody to look after us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The elderly couple that I lived with, they weren't interested in-- in me as a-- as a human being.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they just took their seven and six or whatever it was they got for us, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they were paid to take evacuees, but that's how far it went.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just had one, me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no other children in that house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it-- it's-- I-- I can't blame them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I remember, although I was very young-- I couldn't have been more than-- I must have been 11 and a half or so, I took myself to the doctor and I was in-- I had every symptom and I was in great pain.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he told me I-- I was imagining it and sent me off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next thing was that luckily, this teacher came back from her leave or holiday, whatever it was, looked at me, and just took me straight to hospital.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She could see I was very ill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody else seemed to care.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was in Ely.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
